    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 23.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第23课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A New House.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "新居。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why is the new house special?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这座新房子有什么特别之处？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I had a letter from my sister yesterday.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "昨天我收到了姐姐的一封信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "She lives in Nigeria.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她住在尼日利亚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "In her letter, she said that she would come to England next year.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她在信中说，明年会到英国来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "If she comes, she will get a surprise.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她来了以后，会大吃一惊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "We are now living in a beautiful new house in the country.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们现在住在乡间一栋漂亮的新房子里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Work on it had begun before my sister left.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "姐姐离开前，这座房子就已经动工了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "The house was completed five months ago.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "房子在5个月前竣工。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "In my letter, I told her that she could stay with us.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我在信中告诉她，她可以和我们住在一起。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "The house has many large rooms, and there is a lovely garden.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这座房子有许多宽敞的房间，还有一个可爱的花园。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "It is a very modern house, so it looks strange to some people.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这是一座非常现代化的房子，因此在有些人看来很奇怪。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "It must be the only modern house in the district.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它一定是这个地区唯一的现代化住宅。"
      }
    }
  ],
